  "body": "The prestateTracer reverts the value transfer of a transaction in `result`:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/7a509b47321a28e36f437170a3cc5c283ee7909d/eth/tracers/internal/tracers/prestate_tracer.js#L57-L58\r\n\r\nBut it doesn't revert the gas bought here:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/b211742e5f1ec87e59683e979dd914c1a5a2fade/core/state_transition.go#L167\r\n\r\nand therefore returns the tx sender's balance - (gasPrice * gasLimit).",
